<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #F2F2F2;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .not-footer {
            margin-left: 24px;
            margin-right: 24px;
            margin-top: 24px;

        }
        .content p {
            margin: 16px 0;
            color: #4B5262 !important;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .help-center {
            color: #6ab705;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            flex-direction: column;
            background-color: #f5f7f2;
            color: #4b5262;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 36px 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px;
        }
        img {
            height: 70px;
            width: 200px;
            display: flex;
            margin: auto;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Welcome </title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="not-footer">
        <img src="" alt=""/>

        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
            <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We are excited to have you on board.</p>

            <p>To ensure the security of your account, please confirm that you are the one who initiated this registration.</p>

            <p>If this was you, please click the button below to confirm your account and proceed to login:</p>

            <a href="{{firstLoginLink}}{{token}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
                Confirm My Account
            </a>

            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p> Team</p>
            <p>
                Need Help? Visit our <a href={{url}} class="help-center">Help center.</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            Copyright Â© {{year}} ? .
        </p>
        <p>
            All
            rights reserved.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>